																						<h3>Programs for Educational Institutions</h3>
																						<p class="marginBottom20 ">
																							Academic Volume Licensing programs put Microsoft software in the hands of educators and students so they can interact, collaborate, and learn.
																						</p>
																						<p class="marginBottom20 ">
																							The Academic Volume Licensing program that is best for you depends on the size and type of your institution and how you want to acquire Microsoft licenses. There are two types of programs: Subscription Licensing Programs and Perpetual Licensing Programs.
