																						</p>
																						<p class="marginBottom20 ">
																							<b>Program Change:</b><br>
																							Effective April 1, 2012, the Student Option under Select License and Select Plus will be retired. The Student Option under EES and OVS-ES will not change. No new Student Select 6 enrollments or Student Select Plus Affiliate Registration Forms (ARFs) will be accepted. Enrollments and ARFs current as of March 31, 2012, can stay active for the remainder of the term. However, students cannot order Microsoft Office, Microsoft Office for the Mac, Microsoft Windows 7 Upgrade, or Expressions Studio through a Select Student enrollment or Select Plus ARF as of April 1, 2012. Other products under Student Select and Student Select Plus will be available through the remainder of the term of the enrollment or ARF and can be ordered or downloaded.
																						</p>
																						<p class="marginBottom20 ">
																							Microsoft will continue to work to improve our offerings to students and institutions to provide greater benefits for our institutional customers, administrators, educators and learners. Please contact your software reseller for additional purchasing options for students.
